title: Cows Discography
description:
Discography of the noise rock band Cows. After the group fell apart Shannon Selberg began his own project from music left off the final Cows album, The Heroine Sheiks. Kevin Rutmanis went on to perform in Tomahawk with Mike Patton (Mr. Bungle, Faith No More, Fantomas), Duane Denison (Jesus Lizard) and John Stanier (Helmet, Battles).

contains:
(1987) Taint Pluribus Taint Unum
(1989) Daddy Has a Tail
(1990) Effete and Impudent Snobs
(1991) Peacetika
(1992) Cunning Stunts
(1992) Plowed [EP]
